    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1927-09-20T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1927-09-20T04:00:00-05:00" n="322"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d322">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">863.51/839: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Austria</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Washburn</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-09-20T10:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 20, 1927—10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received September 20—8:25 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>54. The Chancellor has officially and urgently requested me to report that he
                    would appreciate very much an early reply to the question on pages 3 and 4<note
                        n="6" xml:id="d322fn6">The 3d and 5th paragraphs of the preceding
                        despatch.</note> of my despatch No. 1508 of August 30th. The reasons for the
                    urgency of the request are connected with the meeting of the Austrian Control
                    Committee in London on October 11th. Further details are given in my despatch of
                    this date.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washburn</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
